{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "第九回 菩萨和臭虫\n郭大路与燕七分得珠宝后，郭大路想单独行动去找女人，燕七坚持同行。两人进城后，郭大路谎称去找女人，实则不知如何寻找。燕七暗中跟随，两人互相试探。郭大路钱财被骗，流落破庙，与泥菩萨为伴。次日清晨，王动在奎元馆等候，郭大路饿肚子前来。林太平透露黑衣人（一尺七寸剑配四尺剑鞘）未将金狮子等人押送衙门，贼赃也不见了，众人感到奇怪。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们有什么打算？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非你有什么打算？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们的骨头不像你，——有了几个钱就会发痒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是想单独活动？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道没有单独活动过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要走，就走吧，又没有人拉住你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道我连单独活动一天都不行吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说不行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么明天你去不去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道就不能把酒菜从奎元馆买回来请我么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到麦老广的床上去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "答对了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你明天是不是也跟王老大一起去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我今天就跟你一起去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是……我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么回事？有什么地方不舒服。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好像吃坏了，肚子有点不舒服。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看你难过的地方恐怕不是肚子吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实你什么地方难过，我早就清楚得很。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你清楚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道没有这意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道也有这意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然，当然……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我们现在该怎么走呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然是……先到城里去再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我们该怎么走呢，往哪条路走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "往哪条路上走都一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "都一样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪条路上都有女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我在这里等你，你可不能溜呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我当然不会溜的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但哪个才是我要找的那种女人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "干这种事的人，脸上又不会贴着招牌的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人要衣装，佛要金装",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子居然没有在茶馆里等我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道这小子反而先找到路了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然你不仁，我又何妨不义，现在你总不能说我溜了吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人不风流枉少年，这句话你想必也有同感。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来郭兄是想风流风流。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正有此意，只恨找不着上天台的路而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这人难道是天生的穷命？就不能有一天不挨饿的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我为什么要一个人单独行动？为什么要撇开燕七呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "早。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那里臭虫太多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "臭虫？美人窝里怎么会有臭虫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哈，哈哈。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那位姑娘既然对你这样好，一定亲自下厨房，特别弄了不少好东西给你吃，好让你补补元气：，",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到你忽然也变得很有经验了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎么有你这么好的福气呢。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你昨天晚上到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来这小子也会装蒜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "泥菩萨？哪里来的泥菩萨？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 413,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的意思是女菩萨，专门救男人的女菩萨。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 417,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天早上那女菩萨替你做了些什么好东西吃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也没什么好吃的，只不过是些燕窝、鸡汤、面、包子、火腿、蛋……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来你非但艳福齐天，口福也真不错，我却已经快饿死了，非要找个地方吃东西去不可……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到哪里去吃？我陪你去。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不必了，你既然已吃饱，我怎么好意思叫你陪我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，非他妈的要他感动得眼泪直流不可。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王大哥等的人已经来了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还不快起来招呼王大哥的客人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这地方你以前常来么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这还是第一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们要吃什么，说吧，我这就叫他们去起火。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 487,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也照样来一份好了，郭大少呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也来了，还在楼上睡大觉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 507,
      "line_end": 507
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看不出他睡觉的本事倒也不小。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 509,
      "line_end": 509
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你没看到他下楼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 521,
      "line_end": 521
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才这扇窗子是不是开着的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 533,
      "line_end": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "波",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 583,
      "line_end": 583
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么冷的天，哪来的苍蝇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 595,
      "line_end": 595
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "苍蝇虽没有，至少臭虫有几个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 597,
      "line_end": 597
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我在想，这碗面的味道一定不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 607,
      "line_end": 607
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道这碗面为什么特别味道不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 613,
      "line_end": 613
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 615,
      "line_end": 615
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个人我认不认得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 641,
      "line_end": 641
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算不认得，至少总见过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 643,
      "line_end": 643
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 645,
      "line_end": 645
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不知道他是谁，因为我也不认得他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 647,
      "line_end": 647
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么衣服？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 657,
      "line_end": 657
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黑衣服。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 659,
      "line_end": 659
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了他的衣服外，我还认得他的那柄剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 665,
      "line_end": 665
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么样的剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 667,
      "line_end": 667
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一尺七寸长的剑，却配着四尺长的剑鞘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 669,
      "line_end": 669
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你什么时候看到他的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 671,
      "line_end": 671
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们来的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 673,
      "line_end": 673
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你认为这件事很奇怪？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 675,
      "line_end": 675
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你认为不奇怪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 677,
      "line_end": 677
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 687,
      "line_end": 687
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么知道的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 693,
      "line_end": 693
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已经到衙门里去打听过了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 695,
      "line_end": 695
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许他准备将犯人押到别的地方去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 697,
      "line_end": 697
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有犯人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 699,
      "line_end": 699
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有犯人是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 701,
      "line_end": 701
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 715,
      "line_end": 715
    }
